item.title: Proposed Affordable Housing Scheme Lodmore Lane.
item.description: There is a public “Drop in” event to view the proposals and air your views to Adactus (the Housing Assocation). The meeting willl take place on Tuesday March 8th 2016 between 16:00 and 19:00 at Burleydam Community Room.
